# EmbedKit — Project Brief & Completion Status

Original assignment: build a landing page and clickable web app prototype for a document-grounded chatbot builder. **Status: completed** in `frontend/`.

## Original Requirements

- Landing page that communicates product value and drives onboarding
- Chat interface for document upload and in-app bot testing
- Embeddable widget builder with copy/paste embed code
- Paywall with pricing plans and logically gated features
- Additional pages and flows defined in [product.mdc](./product.mdc)

