## Acceptance Checklist

- [x] Landing page communicates value and drives sign-up
- [x] Builder flow: upload docs → test chat → widget preview → copy embed code
- [x] Free tier limits visible: 1 bot, 5 documents, watermark on widget
- [x] Paywall triggers contextually on Pro/Business gates (branding, analytics, second bot, API, document limit)
- [x] Chat UI includes suggested questions, typing indicator, and source citations (mocked)
- [x] `npm run build`, `npm run lint`, and `npm run test` pass from `frontend/`

## Running the Prototype

```bash
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev
```

Open [http://localhost:5173](http://localhost:5173).

## Out of Scope (unchanged)

- RAG / LLM pipeline
- Real authentication and billing
- Functional embed script (snippet UI only)
- `sessionStorage` persistence (documented as optional; not implemented)
